### Test Breeze Wallet Features

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:1011/api/v1

# ===================== Breeze Wallet Packages (Public) =====================

### Get All Breeze Wallet Packages
GET {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/packages

### Get Breeze Wallet Package by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/packages/{{packageId}}

# ===================== Breeze Wallet Packages (Admin Only) =====================

### Create Breeze Wallet Package
POST {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/packages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Starter Pack",
  "amount": 100,
  "price": 9.99,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Create Another Package
POST {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/packages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Premium Pack",
  "amount": 500,
  "price": 39.99,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Update Breeze Wallet Package
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/packages/{{packageId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Starter Pack",
  "amount": 150,
  "price": 14.99
}

### Delete Breeze Wallet Package
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/packages/{{packageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ===================== User Wallet Operations (Authenticated) =====================

### Top Up User's Breeze Wallet
POST {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/top-up
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "packageId": "{{packageId}}"
}

### Get User's Wallet Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/breeze-wallet/balance/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

